[*] [b]PCP_FarmingCompat.lua[/b] — Farming spray registration module removed (no longer needed).
[*] [b]Spray loot distributions[/b] — 7 distribution entries removed (CrateFertilizer, FarmerTruckBed, GardenStoreMisc).
[/list]

[h3]Added[/h3]
[list]
