[h2]v1.5.2 — Filter Degradation Fix (2026-03-09)[/h2]

[h3]Bug Fixes[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Filter degradation crash on crafting[/b] — Safe-variant hazard recipes (methanol distillation, KOH synthesis, etc.) produced stack traces because filter degradation tried DrainableComboItem methods on Clothing-type gas masks. Fixed in PhobosLib 1.18.2 with condition-based degradation.
[*] Requires [b]PhobosLib 1.18.2+[/b] (was 1.18.1+)
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]v1.5.1 — Distribution Key Hotfix (2026-03-09)[/h2]

[h3]Bug Fixes[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Server crash on startup[/b] — Fixed RuntimeException crash on B42.14.1 multiplayer dedicated servers caused by 4 invalid distribution keys (StoreCounterSmoke, GardenStorageMisc, RestaurantKitchen, GroceryStoreSnacks). Replaced with correct B42 equivalents. Added BarShelfLiquor for SimpleSugarSyrup.
[*] [b]Nil-guard helper[/b] — All distribution inserts now safely skip missing keys instead of crashing, preventing future breakage if B42 renames or removes distribution tables.
[/list]

