[h2]v1.5.0 — Chewing Tobacco Curing & Tag System (2026-03-09)[/h2]

[h3]New Features[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Dual-path chewing tobacco curing[/b] — Prepare Chewing Tobacco Mix (tobacco + salt + sweetener + alkali + water), then choose: fire-cure on a heat source (instant) or seal in a jar for 14-day fermentation. Both paths produce the same chewing tobacco.
[*] [b]4 new items[/b] — ChewingTobaccoMixRaw, SealedChewingTobaccoJar, CuredChewingTobaccoJar, ChewingTobacco
[*] [b]Custom ItemTag system[/b] — 382 recipe OR-list inputs converted to 4 registered tags (protective gloves, goggles, respirators, acid-resistant vessels). New PPE items are automatically recognised.
[*] [b]Pouch of Hemp & vanilla tobacco[/b] — HempLoose drainable and vanilla TobaccoLoose integrated into pipe and tobacco recipes
[*] [b]Farming spray tooltips[/b] — Plain-English descriptions on spray items explaining which crop problems they treat and how to use them
[*] [b]4 Dynamic Trading sandbox toggles[/b] — New PCP_DynamicTrading settings page with per-sub-category toggles for botanical trade items (Material, Medical, Survival, Literature). Requires Dynamic Trading mod; no effect without it.
[/list]

[h3]Changed[/h3]
[list]
[*] 3 deprecated items (ChewingTobaccoTin, ChewingTobaccoWaterTin, ChewingTobaccoJar) — save migration converts to ChewingTobacco
[*] Cork input removed from all 67 lab recipes — aligns with ZVV which no longer uses cork stoppers
[*] Tradeable items: 67 to [b]76[/b] (9 horticulture routing fixes + 4 new botanical items)
[*] Sandbox options: 52 to [b]66[/b] (+4 DT botanical toggles + 10 from v1.4.0 hemp effects)
[*] Requires [b]PhobosLib 1.18.1+[/b] (was 1.18.0+)
[/list]

[h3]Bug Fixes[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Farming spray context menu[/b] — Custom spray options now correctly appear in the "Treat Problem" submenu (fixed in PhobosLib 1.18.1)
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h2]v1.4.0 — Medicinal Effects & Moodle Framework (2026-03-08)[/h2]

[h3]New Features[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Medicated custom moodle[/b] — Medicinal hemp items (poultice, tincture) trigger a Medicated moodle via Moodle Framework integration. Configurable duration. Graceful no-op when Moodle Framework is not installed.
[*] [b]Medicinal timed actions[/b] — Poultice and tincture now have timed application actions with visual and audio feedback instead of instant use.
[*] [b]Hemp product effects system[/b] — Doubled base effects on hemp products. New effects on decarboxylated buds and sugar syrup.
[*] [b]33 new sandbox options[/b] — New PCP_HempEffects settings page with per-product stat tuning for pipes, cigars, cigarettes, decarbed buds, poultice, tincture, sugar syrup, plus moodle duration controls.
[*] [b]EnableDebugLogging sandbox option[/b] — Centralised debug logging via PhobosLib_Debug.
[*] [b]Fermentation tooltip[/b] — Canned hemp buds show dynamic curing progress (%) and estimated days remaining. Canning date stamped on creation and displayed in tooltip.
[*] [b]Improved static tooltips[/b] — Explicit ~4 week curing duration and "not spoilage" clarification on fermentable items.
[/list]

[h3]Bug Fixes[/h3]
[list]
[*] [b]Cigar recipe[/b] — Now uses tobacco leaves + sugar with partial sugar consumption (was incorrectly consuming full sugar item).
[*] [b]Horticulture migration re-runnable[/b] — Migration sandbox flag can now be re-enabled for repeated use.
[*] [b]Drainable migration RuntimeException[/b] — Fixed crash in drainable item migration path.
[/list]

[h3]Changed[/h3]
[list]
[*] Sandbox options: 19 to [b]52[/b] (+33 on PCP_HempEffects page)
[*] Requires [b]PhobosLib 1.18.0+[/b] (was 1.16.0+)
[*] Optional: [b]Moodle Framework[/b] (new soft dependency)
[/list]

